      strategies: ['Label: "Panic attack. Not dangerous. Will pass."', 'Physiological sigh \u2014 2 short inhales through nose, 1 long exhale through mouth (x4)', 'TIPP \u2014 cold water on face, intense exercise (30 jumping jacks), paced breathing, paired muscle relaxation', '5-4-3-2-1 sensory grounding', 'Hold ice cubes or cold can', 'Sit on the floor \u2014 closer to gravity helps', 'Do not run from it (panic chases avoidance) \u2014 wait it out', 'Avoid coffee, weed, alcohol during recovery'],
